<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الجَاثِيَةُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مُسْتَوْفِزِينَ عَلَى الرُّكَبِ.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> ﴿نَسْتَنْسِخُ﴾ نَكْتُبُ ﴿نَنْسَاكُمْ﴾ نَتْرُكُكُمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>﴿وَمَا يُهْلِكُنَا إِلا الدَّهْرُ﴾ الْآيَةَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>